source.name: DLA No FEAR Act Summary Statistics
source.description: DLA presents summary statistical data pursuant to the Notification and Federal Employee Antidiscrimination and Retaliation Act of 2002 (No Fear Act).  The Equal Employment Opportunity (EEO) data required to be posted by the No FEAR Act contains statistics pertaining to complaints of employment discrimination filed against it by employees, former employees and applicants for employment.
